"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of pin code input"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSPinCodeInput","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllPinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PinceCodeInputComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"pin code input","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pin code input"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of dimensions (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"type":"image","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"Theme Orange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}